locality: China Village land, ca. 190 m NNE WCS/SCHP Timbwa Camp.

Ca. 35 km W of Matai on Matai - Kasanga road, ca 0.4 km S of road in open miombo woodland on lower slopes of Lwasu Hills near Kalombo River Forest Reserve. On rocky piles, sandy soils and large termite mounds.
South Viphya, North of Elephant Rock on main road.
